title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Mosquito XE Helicopter Project - version 02d
description:
In this video we are going to look at the Mosquito XE Helicopter which is a single seater helicopter which is still under development. We looked earlier at the helicopter but since then it already received two new updates so let's see what has been improved.

If you would like to try Mosquito XE Helicopter Project yourself download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/29050/mosquito-xe-helicopter-project-wip
